创建一个 Terraform 模块，为 tfvars 文件中列出的每个指定分支创建一个嵌套的 for_each 循环，按照以下步骤操作：

1. 创建一个 `variables.tf` 文件，用于存储模块中使用的变量：

```hcl
variable "branches" {
  type        = list(string)
  description = "要为其创建资源的分支列表"
}
```

2. 创建您的模块的 `main.tf` 文件。在这个示例中，我将使用嵌套的 for_each 创建 AWS CodePipeline 资源：

```hcl
resource "aws_codecommit_repository" "this" {
  for_each = { for branch in var.branches : branch => branch }

  repository_name = each.key
}

resource "aws_codepipeline" "this" {
  for_each = { for branch in var.branches : branch => branch }

  name     = "${each.key}-pipeline"
  role_arn = aws_iam_role.codepipeline.arn

  artifact_store {
    location = aws_s3_bucket.artifact_store.bucket
    type     = "S3"
  }

  stage {
    name = "Source"

    action {
      name             = "Source"
      action_type_owner = "AWS"
      provider         = "CodeCommit"
      version          = "1"

      configuration = {
        RepositoryName = aws_codecommit_repository.this[each.key].repository_name
        BranchName     = each.key
      }

      output_artifacts = ["source_output"]
    }
  }

  # 可以在这里添加额外的阶段，比如 "Build" 和 "Deploy"
}

locals {
  branch_map = { for branch in var.branches : branch => aws_codepipeline.this[branch] }
}
```

3. 创建一个 `outputs.tf` 文件来输出创建的资源：

```hcl
output "codecommit_repositories" {
  description = "创建的 AWS CodeCommit 存储库"
  value       = aws_codecommit_repository.this
}

output "codepipelines" {
  description = "创建的 AWS CodePipelines"
  value       = aws_codepipeline.this
}
```

4. 创建一个 `versions.tf` 文件来指定 Terraform 和提供程序的版本：

```hcl
terraform {
  required_version = ">= 0.13"

  required_providers {
    aws = {
      source  = "hashicorp/aws"
      version = "~> 3.0"
    }
  }
}
```

5. 创建一个 `terraform.tfvars` 文件来指定分支列表：

```hcl
branches = ["branch1", "branch2", "branch3"]
```

6. 最后，创建您的根 `main.tf` 文件并调用您的模块：

```hcl
module "my_module" {
  source   = "./module_directory"
  branches = var.branches
}

variable "branches" {
  default = []
}
```

将 `./module_directory` 替换为包含 `main.tf` 文件的模块路径。

